  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_96df5526055f4bbc995b018146d4b3b7">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Letters, photographs, scrapbooks, and other materials concerning the Civil War and Civil War veterans.Civil War items collected by James V. Scaife.  Items include lithographed Civil War covers; letters to Scaife concerning Civil War research; photographs of battle fields; scrapbooks of newspaper clippings concerning the Civil War and other events in American history; roster of attendance of the Wilder's Brigade reunion at Chattanooga in 1913; obituaries and other clippings pertaining to Civil War veterans; and other printed items.</p>  </scopecontent>
